<item>
            <title>[LU-944] Test failure on test suite replay-ost-single, subtest test_0b</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-944</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for Chris Gearing &amp;lt;chris@whamcloud.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/08bf83f4-2a8f-11e1-a412-5254004bbbd3&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/08bf83f4-2a8f-11e1-a412-5254004bbbd3&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_0b failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Restart of ost6 failed!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Info required for matching: replay-ost-single 0b&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_1 failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;error creating /mnt/lustre/d0.replay-ost-single/f1&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Info required for matching: replay-ost-single 1&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_2 failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;error creating /mnt/lustre/d0.replay-ost-single/f1&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Info required for matching: replay-ost-single 2&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_3 failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;test failed to respond and timed out&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Info required for matching: replay-ost-single 3&lt;/p&gt;</description>
